      "role": "user",
      "content": "reframe it? how? every single thing i built is gone. it's not just a \"setback,\" it's a total collapse. my parents worked their whole lives to give me a chance and i just burned it all. the shame is so heavy i can't even breathe sometimes. it feels like there's no version of the future where this doesn't follow me forever. it just feels like the debt and the failure are who i am now.",
