      "content": "but they wont. they'll just look at me with pity or disappointment. i can already see it in my head. the \"how could you\" looks in their eyes. i feel like a burden that just needs to be cleared away. if i'm gone, at least the debt won't be my problem anymore and they won't have to deal with the wreckage i've caused. i just want the noise to stop. it feels like the only way to actually fix the shame is to just not exist in it anymore.",
